
Hi, this is my first example with gem 'fpm'.

It allows you to deploy a tar.gz as a debian package (or RPM!)

I guess this is probably overkill because I start from sources, but...

It's ok.


= INSTALL =

Prerequisites:

  sudo apt-get install ruby-full
	gem install fpm

To build:

  make

To install:

  make installa

= Credits =

Thanks to aturli for pointing out this gem!

